723109f-a.text:
72 to 78 St. Mark's Place, (East 8th Street), south side, between Second and Firnt Aves., showing (No. 74) The Stuyvesant Neighborhood House, Clara Buttenwieser Unger Memorial. No. 72 (extreme right), has been joined to No. 74 and remodeled to constitute a single 4-story unit, now (1937) bearing
the Nos. 72-74.
July 24, 1930.
P. L. Sperr.
